channel.title: Cpu rises to 100% when i start my server
channel.description:
My CPU % Is completely normal but when i click run on my server and when it actually runs, it rises to100% and it stays that way, causing lag\server crashes. And this has become to be a very annoying problem, as it is beyond my knowledge of what is going on, So if anyone could try and fix this, i would appreciate it.

Cpu After Server is Run
